Once upon a time in a forest there lived a monkey who resided on a berry tree which was on the bank of river.
And in thant river lived crocodile and his wife.One day crocodile came to the bank of the river and rested 
under the berry tree.The kind-hearted monkey offered him some berries. The crocodile came back for more berry as he loved them.
As the day passed by the crocodile and the monkey became goog friends.One day sent some berries for the crocodile's
wife.She ate the berries and loved them and wondered that if the berries are so sweet how sweet the monkey's heart would be.
The next day she told her husband that she wants to eat monkey's heart the crocodile was surpised and said that monkey was his very good friend
but the wife blackmailed him that she would die if she doesn't get the monkey's heart.